Ysis Amariele Sonkeng (amụrụ n'abalị̀ iri abụo nke onwa Septemba afọ 1989, Baleveng) bụ onye Cameroon na-agba bọọlụ ụmụ nwanyị, onye na-agba nye otu egwuregwu bọọlụ mba Cameroon na otu Louves Minproff de Yaoundé Ọ na-agba  egwuregwu bọọlụ dị ka onye na-akwado onye oche goolu ma na agbachit ndị otu ya ka a hapụ onye goolu na-egwuregwu n'afọ 2012 Summer Olympics. A maara ya maka ịgbanye goolu nke onwe  na ogbugbu bọọlụ megide ndị mba New Zealand.
